---

---

<section class="hero card">
	<div class="hero__copy">
		<h1 class="hero__title">
			<span class="hero__title-primary">TARO</span>
			<span class="hero__title-secondary">Communication</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="hero__subtitle">
			Hi. I'm Sean “Taro” Wang，也就是芋头王。
			这里是我对世界和自己发出的通讯文稿合集。欢迎光临。
		</p>

		<div class="hero__actions">
			<a class="button-link" href="#latest">看最新文章</a>
			<a class="button-link secondary" href="/about">认识一下 TARO</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="hero__profile">
		<img class="hero__avatar" src="/taaowang.png" alt="Taro Wang" />
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(16rem, 0.7fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
		min-height: 30rem;
	}

	.hero__copy {
		align-self: end;
		max-width: 42rem;
	}

	.hero__title {
		margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.08em;
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 5.3vw, 4.8rem);
		font-weight: 500;
		line-height: 0.92;
		letter-spacing: -0.045em;
		max-width: 10.4ch;
	}

	.hero__title span {
		display: block;
	}

	.hero__title-primary {
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.hero__title-secondary {
		font-size: 0.88em;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	.hero__subtitle {
		max-width: 42rem;
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		line-height: 1.95;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.hero__actions {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.9rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.hero__profile {
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background:
			linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28)),
			linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-soft), var(--highlight-soft));
		border-radius: calc(var(--radius-lg) - 6px);
	}

	.hero__avatar {
		width: min(100%, 17rem);
		aspect-ratio: 1;
		object-fit: contain;
		background: var(--bg-strong);
		border-radius: 1.4rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		box-shadow: var(--surface-shadow);
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.hero {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			min-height: unset;
		}

		.hero__profile {
			place-items: center;
		}
	}
</style>
